name: Empty Pallete
description:
A simple 6 levels platformer made for Mini Jam 127: Cats².

Controls:
  • WASD / ZQSD / Arrow keys : Move
  • J : Run
  • K : Jump
Credits: Art:

- Level 1 and 2 backgrounds: https://florassence.itch.io/garden-backgrounds
by florassence: https://twitter.com/florassence

- Level 3 background generated by: https://deep-fold.itch.io/space-background-generator

- Level 4 background: https://sim-kaart.itch.io/atmospheric-pixel-art-background-images-of-space-desti... by Sim Kaart: https://twitter.com/simkaart_

- Level 5 background: https://ansimuz.itch.io/mountain-dusk-parallax-background by ansimuz: https://twitter.com/ansimuz

- Level 6 background: https://swapnilrane24.itch.io/night-background-2 by MadFireOn: https://swapnilrane24.itch.io/

- cat sprites derived from: https://opengameart.org/content/cat-sprites by Shepardskin: https://twitter.com/Shepardskin

- Color rectangles from the jam page: https://itch.io/jam/mini-jam-127-cats

Font:

DePixel: https://www.dafont.com/depixel.font by Ingo Zimmermann [ingoFonts]: https://www.dafont.com/profile.php?user=78288
